          <OMSTR>Have fun, it&apos;s math! Answer the questions below by typing your answers directly into this document. Save your work frequently so you don&apos;t lose it if Lurch locks up or crashes (pressing CTRL+S on Windows or CMD+S on Mac saves your document instantly, so press it often). You are not required to bubble anything on this exam, but you can if you want to.  This is a take-home exam, and so must be completed without any collaboration.  You can ask me any questions you want but you cannot discuss the exam with anyone else (including each other).  You cannot use any internet or other online resources or references, but you can use our lecture notes, previous homework problems, examples and notes done in class, and anything in your Dropbox folder.</OMSTR>
